public class UserIO
extends DX_IOTT

An extention of the DX_IOTT structure that is used when performing user defined input/output actions.

fhandleMark

private static int fhandleMark
Internal counter of the number of UserIO objects that have been created since the JVM was initialized. Used to set the io_fhandle member at initialization time.

refList

List of soft references to all of the current UserIO objects. Used by the DX class to map the supplied file descriptor to an object.
